WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:02.870
《越狱》  前情回顾
Previously on Prison Break.

00:02.870 --> 00:05.050
你得了下丘脑错构瘤
You have hypothalamus Hamartoma,

00:05.050 --> 00:06.790
医生认为你需要手术
the doctor feels you need surgery

00:06.810 --> 00:08.130
否则  你会死
Otherwise you could die

00:08.130 --> 00:09.680
你不听命令吗
You are not following direct orders?

00:09.680 --> 00:12.000
我听命令  长官
Oh, I'm following direct orders, sir.

00:12.740 --> 00:14.100
只不过不听你的了
Just not from you anymore.

00:14.100 --> 00:17.240
如果不是你  我就死在这张桌子上了
I would've died on this table if it weren't for you, Doc.

00:17.240 --> 00:19.000
干嘛
What?

00:19.000 --> 00:20.600
该回家了
Time to come home now.

00:20.600 --> 00:22.570
你要帮我找一个新的买家
You're going to help me find a new buyer for Scylla.

00:22.570 --> 00:25.100
他叫怀肯  他不是买家  是个中间人
His name is Vikan, and he's not a buyer, he's a conduit.

00:25.100 --> 00:26.640
我们走吧
Let's go.

00:26.640 --> 00:27.740
巴格维尔留在这里
And Bagwell's staying here.

00:27.740 --> 00:29.500
我警告过你别耍我
I warned you not to screw me over.

00:29.500 --> 00:31.870
别来无恙  格雷琴  他是谁
It's been a long time, Gretchen. Who's he?

00:31.870 --> 00:33.370
"锡拉"在我手上
I'm the guy that's holding Scylla.

00:33.370 --> 00:36.870
这是不完整的  少了一个部件  小子
It's incomplete. There's a piece missing, slick.

00:39.440 --> 00:41.200
你好啊  唐
Hello, Don.

00:41.200 --> 00:43.670
我相信你拿了我的东西
I believe you have something that belongs to me.

00:43.670 --> 00:45.940
过来拿吧
Come and get it.

00:55.640 --> 00:58.540
你应该知道  这不是什么灵丹妙药
Just so it's fresh in your mind, this isn't a magic elixir.

00:58.540 --> 01:00.800
你还是要去医院
You still need a hospital.

01:00.800 --> 01:03.170
你需要真正的仪器
You need real equipment.

01:03.170 --> 01:05.200
或者找一个
Could probably use a doctor

01:05.200 --> 01:06.840
有医疗执照的医生
who's still got a license to practice medicine.

01:06.840 --> 01:08.840
首先  我们要找回"锡拉"
First we get Scylla.

01:08.840 --> 01:12.070
然后  我才去医院
Then I'll go to the hospital.

01:51.400 --> 01:52.400
你弄完了吗
You finished?

01:52.400 --> 01:54.700
差不多了
Just about.

02:00.400 --> 02:02.370
你现在准备说话了
So, I take it you're ready to talk now?

02:02.370 --> 02:03.770
事实上  我准备好和你见面了
Actually, I'm ready to meet.

02:03.770 --> 02:05.840
我有一个更好的主意
I got a better idea.

02:13.200 --> 02:14.670
所有人都出去
Everyone out!

02:25.570 --> 02:26.770
你被包围了
You're surrounded.

02:26.770 --> 02:29.270
把"锡拉"部件交出来  迈克尔
Come out with your piece of Scylla, Michael.

02:29.270 --> 02:30.540
你先交
You first.

02:32.100 --> 02:34.100
出来吧  不然  我就用烟把你们熏出来
Come out, or I'm going to gas you out.

02:34.100 --> 02:38.770
如果你们被熏出来  我有满满的一梭子子弹
If it's the latter, I have a full magazine with 30 rounds.

02:38.770 --> 02:41.300
想赌一把  看是不是有人跑得比你快
Want to bet at least one of them could outrun you?

02:41.300 --> 02:43.140
你凭什么认为  我把部件带在身上
What makes you think I'd even keep the piece on me?

02:43.140 --> 02:44.340
我了解你  迈克尔
Oh, I know you, Michael.

02:44.340 --> 02:46.070
你随身带着那块东西
You're not letting that thing out of your sight.

02:46.070 --> 02:48.000
我还是那句话
I stand by my original offer.

02:48.000 --> 02:49.100
过来拿吧
Come and get it.

02:49.100 --> 02:50.570
好吧
Okay.

02:54.570 --> 02:56.440
趴低点  等烟升到天花板
Stay low. Let the gas rise to the ceiling.

02:56.440 --> 02:58.670
这里空间很大  但是  在我们窒息前
This is a big space, but it won't take many more of those

02:58.670 --> 03:00.100
撑不了多久
before we start to asphyxiate.

03:00.100 --> 03:01.600
林肯在哪
Where's Lincoln?!

03:03.300 --> 03:06.070
还多着呢  迈克尔
Here we go, Michael.

