03:38.200 --> 03:40.160
《越狱》第四季 第十四集
Prison.Break.S04E14

03:49.340 --> 03:51.470
好了  我们现在开车去拿"锡拉"
All right, now we take a ride and we pick up Scylla.

03:51.470 --> 03:52.800
不然  我就一枪崩了你
Or I put a bullet in your head.

03:52.800 --> 03:54.170
不可能
It ain't gonna happen.

03:54.170 --> 03:55.600
试试看
Try me.

04:02.070 --> 04:03.800
大家早
Good morning.

04:05.840 --> 04:09.240
现在  大家都被枪指着
Okay, all right, now that we all have guns pointed at us,

04:09.240 --> 04:10.300
我们谈谈吧  好吗
let's talk, okay?

04:10.300 --> 04:11.670
说吧
Fine.

04:11.670 --> 04:15.700
你先告诉我  我到底是在和谁说话  是唐吗
You could start by telling me who I'm talking to, Don?

04:15.700 --> 04:17.270
我在过去17年里
You're talking to a guy who spent 17 years

04:17.270 --> 04:20.070
规规矩矩为政府卖命
in service of his government, all by the book.

04:20.070 --> 04:22.140
你知道  这些值多少钱吗
You know what the sum total of it was?

04:22.140 --> 04:23.870
一文不值  什么都不是
Nothing. Nada.

04:23.870 --> 04:25.370
我们是一类人  迈克尔
But we're very similar, Michael,

04:25.370 --> 04:26.700
而且  从根本来说  我们要的是同一样东西
and fundamentally, we want the same thing.

04:26.700 --> 04:28.370
我有方法拿到手
And I have a way to get it.

04:28.370 --> 04:29.770
什么意思
How's that?

04:29.770 --> 04:31.170
我找了一个"锡拉"买家
I got a buyer for Scylla.

04:31.170 --> 04:33.870
一个和你一样  想搞垮"公司"的人
A guy who wants to destroy the Company as much as you do.

04:33.870 --> 04:35.970
他愿意付一大笔钱
And he's willing to pay a lot of money for it.

04:35.970 --> 04:37.540
多少钱
How much?

04:37.540 --> 04:41.140
你选一个国外帐号  九位数
Nine figures in an offshore account of your choosing.

04:41.840 --> 04:42.900
就是这样
So, there it is.

04:42.900 --> 04:44.370
或者
Or...

04:44.370 --> 04:46.370
你可以继续按你的原则办事
you could stand by your principles.

04:46.370 --> 04:47.900
我不干
I'll pass.

04:48.640 --> 04:50.070
我是骗了你  我承认
Look, I burned you, right?

04:50.070 --> 04:52.070
我道歉  但是  有意义吗
And I'd apologize, but what's the point?

04:52.070 --> 04:55.240
我们的处境都很尴尬
We're all out in the cold now.

04:55.240 --> 04:56.270
但是  我们不可能一直躲着"公司"
But we're not going to be able to hide from the Company

04:56.270 --> 04:57.370
我们根本没有本钱
on a shoestring budget.

04:57.370 --> 04:58.570
谁是买家
Who's the buyer?

04:58.570 --> 05:00.270
他以前在"公司"做事  有过节
He's an ex-Company guy with a bone to pick.

05:00.270 --> 05:01.800
和你爸一样
Just like your father.

05:01.800 --> 05:03.900
迈克尔
Michael?

05:03.900 --> 05:07.370
我要先和他见面
I'd need to meet him first.

05:07.370 --> 05:08.700
可以安排
That can be arranged.

05:08.700 --> 05:10.570
只是想告诉你
And just so you know, this...

05:10.570 --> 05:12.740
这不是私人恩怨  只是笔交易
This wasn't personal. This is just business.

05:12.740 --> 05:14.540
我会和你联络的
We'll be in touch.

05:31.840 --> 05:33.770
我们还是按原计划行事
We stick to the plan, all right?

05:33.770 --> 05:35.270
我们会拿回"锡拉"
We're going to get Scylla.

05:35.270 --> 05:37.270
只要等阿历克斯那头打通关系
We wait for Alex to come through on his end.

05:37.270 --> 05:39.070
好吗
All right?

05:57.600 --> 05:59.200
你好  阿历克斯
Hello, Alex.

06:00.840 --> 06:02.170
你来了
You came.

06:02.170 --> 06:04.340
我一向遵守承诺
I always do,

06:04.340 --> 06:07.040
就算会被扣工钱
to the detriment of my pay grade.

06:08.940 --> 06:10.370
过去几个星期
These last few weeks,

06:10.370 --> 06:11.970
我参与了一起秘密行动
I've been part of an off-the-books operation

06:11.970 --> 06:13.940
是国安局安排的
under the hand of Homeland Security.

06:15.140 --> 06:17.200
费丽舍  和我共事的人
Felicia, the people I'm working with,

06:17.200 --> 06:18.770
我们就差那么一点
we're this close to coming up with

06:18.770 --> 06:20.440
就能得到摧毁"公司"的东西
the one thing that can destroy the Company:

06:20.440 --> 06:24.140
他们的黑皮书  我们能搞到手  里面有姓名  数字
their little black book. We can get it. Names, numbers.

06:24.140 --> 06:27.470
我可不想夹在部门间的斗争里
Look, I don't want to get caught up in some interagency politics.

06:27.470 --> 06:28.940
如果这次国安局的行动
So, if this is Homeland's show...

06:28.940 --> 06:31.870
国安局终止了行动  我们不能再回去了
Homeland buried the operation. We can't come back in.

06:31.870 --> 06:33.840
但是  我们还可以搞垮"公司"
But we could still take the Company down.

06:33.840 --> 06:35.870
所以  我的问题是
So, my question to you is:

06:35.870 --> 06:38.200
在联调局里  你认为可以信任谁
Who do you know in the Bureau that you can trust?

06:38.200 --> 06:40.140
以前是你  阿历克斯
It used to be you, Alex.

06:41.900 --> 06:44.170
过去几个月  我失去了很多东西
I've lost a lot of things these last few months,

06:44.170 --> 06:46.340
不止是你的信任
not the least of which is your trust.

06:46.340 --> 06:48.340
但我不是来乞求你的
But I don't come to you hat in hand.

06:48.340 --> 06:51.400
"锡拉"是存在的
Scylla is real.

06:51.400 --> 06:53.870
如果你不想扯上关系  我可以理解
But if you don't want anything to do with it, it's okay.

06:53.870 --> 06:56.770
没事  我可以离开
It's all right; I could walk away.

07:00.400 --> 07:04.900
有一个人也许能帮你
Yeah, there is someone who might be able to help.

07:07.800 --> 07:12.940
长官  洛杉矶有超过1千万人口
Sir, there are over ten million faces in Los Angeles.

07:12.940 --> 07:15.670
加上安全局和情报局的卫星  我们需要过滤
Even with NSA and CIA satellite links, we're going to be sifting

07:15.670 --> 07:17.870
几百万G的图像数据
through millions of gigabytes of image data.

07:17.870 --> 07:19.670
找到唐·赛尔夫
The chances of finding Don Self,

07:19.670 --> 07:21.670
斯科菲尔德和布伦斯的几率  不是很高
Scofield and Burrows... it's not good.

07:21.670 --> 07:23.000
让我们增加几率
Well, let's improve the odds.

07:23.000 --> 07:24.540
赛尔夫和兄弟俩
Self and the brothers

07:24.540 --> 07:26.540
是偷了"锡拉"  但是
may have stolen Scylla but none of them have

07:26.540 --> 07:28.200
他们没有任何办法出售
the connections to off-load it.

07:28.200 --> 07:31.440
在查找中加上格雷琴的脸
Add Gretchen's face to the search.

07:31.440 --> 07:34.140
她不可能是斯科菲尔德小组的一员
She won't be welcome in Scofield's camp.

07:34.140 --> 07:36.370
把她和赛尔夫的图像联系到一起
So, connect her image with Self's.

07:36.370 --> 07:38.940
如果在洛杉矶任何5尺距离内
We find those two within five feet of each other

07:38.940 --> 07:42.640
找到他们  我们就能找到"锡拉"
anywhere in Los Angeles, and we've found Scylla.

07:51.900 --> 07:54.870
你是格雷琴阿姨的朋友吗
Are you friends with my Auntie Gretchen?

07:56.070 --> 07:59.640
去你的房间玩  妈妈一会就过去
Go play in your room. Mommy will be in soon.

08:06.770 --> 08:09.300
她爸爸在哪
Where's her daddy?

08:10.800 --> 08:12.570
格雷琴从来不提及他
Gretchen doesn't talk about him.

08:12.570 --> 08:15.800
艾米丽还不知道你不是她的
So, Emily doesn't know that you ain't...

08:15.800 --> 08:18.470
格雷琴是她妈妈
That Gretchen's her mama?

08:18.470 --> 08:21.000
不  我宁愿保持这种方式
No, and I'd like to keep it that way.

08:28.970 --> 08:30.670
可爱的孩子
Cute girl.

08:33.740 --> 08:35.700
不要伤害我的孩子
Don't hurt my little girl.

08:36.970 --> 08:39.370
如果你要做什么  冲我来吧
If you have to do something, do it to me.

08:42.040 --> 08:43.900
你以为我是什么人
What do you think I am?

08:43.900 --> 08:45.770
野兽
A monster?

08:45.770 --> 08:48.570
你把我们囚禁在我们家里
You're holding us prisoner in our own home.

08:48.570 --> 08:52.270
我和你们一样  都是囚犯
I'm just as much a prisoner as you.

08:54.800 --> 08:59.200
奶白色  黑体字
Eggshell white. Bold lettering.

08:59.200 --> 09:01.570
双层浮花  我曾经是科尔·普发
Double embossed. I was Cole Pfeiffer.

09:01.570 --> 09:03.200
受人尊敬的商人
Respected businessman.

09:03.200 --> 09:05.400
东北区域最好的推销员
Top salesman in the Northeast Region.

09:07.640 --> 09:10.340
现在  我又变回过去的
Now I'm back being prisoner

09:10.340 --> 09:12.000
囚犯身份
of my own identity.

09:12.000 --> 09:17.040
帝博格·巴格维尔  罪犯
Theodore Bagwell. Convict.

09:18.640 --> 09:23.570
管他呢  江山易改  本性难移  对吧
To hell with it. We are who we are, right?

09:26.170 --> 09:28.170
你是卖什么的
What were you selling?

09:28.170 --> 09:30.500
你管不着
Never you mind.

09:30.500 --> 09:33.100
你只要祈祷你妹妹能脱险
You just pray your sister comes through.

09:35.340 --> 09:37.170
"公司"被搞垮  我们拿到钱
The Company gets destroyed  and we get paid.

09:37.170 --> 09:38.740
这买卖其实不错
It's a great deal.

09:38.740 --> 09:41.000
这个人只会是另一个克兰兹将军
This guy is just another General Krantz waiting to happen.

09:41.000 --> 09:43.140
假设我们把"锡拉"买给他  这个"公司"倒了
Let's say we do sell it to him and the Company burns,

09:43.140 --> 09:44.540
你知道接下来会怎样吗
You know what happens then?

09:44.540 --> 09:48.240
另一个"公司"会在前者之上建立
Another company is built right on top of that one.

09:48.240 --> 09:50.740
我们不卖
We're not selling.

10:01.260 --> 10:02.740
我进去了
I'm in.

10:02.740 --> 10:04.240
苏克雷搞定了
Sucre pulled it off.

10:04.240 --> 10:06.170
好极了
Great.

10:10.700 --> 10:12.620
找出地点
Get an address.

10:24.840 --> 10:26.140
有用吗
Is this going to work?

10:26.140 --> 10:27.240
这就象超声波
It's like an ultrasound.

10:27.240 --> 10:29.470
能透视所有东西
It can see through everything.

10:43.500 --> 10:45.260
你这是增大耐药量
You're building up a tolerance.

10:45.260 --> 10:48.000
那就加大剂量
Then we'll up the dosage.

10:48.000 --> 10:49.730
对  我增加了
Yeah, I have,

10:49.730 --> 10:51.060
但这样的话  大剂量会比肿瘤本身
and at this point, a higher dosage would have

10:51.060 --> 10:53.560
带来更多的副作用
more side effects than the tumor itself.

10:53.560 --> 10:55.600
我会尽量不用它
I'll manage without it.

10:55.600 --> 10:56.960
你坐在这等着
Sit this one out.

10:56.960 --> 10:58.500
让我和苏克雷来处理
Let me and Sucre handle it.

10:58.500 --> 10:59.860
我也去
I'm going.

11:07.800 --> 11:10.660
他怎么就不理解  我要结束这一切
Why can't he understand I need to finish this?

11:10.660 --> 11:12.300
所发生的一切
Everything that happened,

11:12.300 --> 11:14.630
都是"公司"引起的
it all started with the Company.

11:14.630 --> 11:17.000
也许林肯不这么认为
Maybe not for Lincoln.

11:17.000 --> 11:18.360
也许对他来说  这一切
Maybe for him, this all started

11:18.360 --> 11:21.000
是从他弟弟救他越狱开始的
with his little brother breaking him out of prison.

11:21.000 --> 11:23.360
迈克尔  你救了他的命
Michael, you saved his life.

11:23.360 --> 11:25.030
如果你有什么不测
If anything happens to you,

11:25.030 --> 11:27.700
他下辈子都会愧疚
he spends the rest of his life feeling guilty for that.

11:27.700 --> 11:29.700
告诉我
Tell me something,

11:29.700 --> 11:32.260
什么时候一件高尚的事变成了狂热盲从
at what point does a noble deed become fanaticism?

11:32.260 --> 11:35.260
狂热是打败他们的唯一方法
Fanaticism is the only way to beat them.

11:35.260 --> 11:37.060
即使为此丧命吗
Even if it kills you?

11:51.000 --> 11:53.400
打开车尾箱
Hey, pop the trunk.

12:18.860 --> 12:21.050
方特罗伊旅店停车场
Fauntleroy Hotel Parking only.

12:34.560 --> 12:36.160
迈克尔
Micheal?

12:37.700 --> 12:40.360
苏克雷刚发了条信息  他发现格雷琴和赛尔夫了
Sucre just sent a text. He's found Gretchen and Self.

12:40.360 --> 12:42.830
很好  很好
Good, good.

12:42.830 --> 12:44.560
你没事吧
You all right?

12:44.560 --> 12:46.060
目前还好
Yeah, for now.

12:46.060 --> 12:47.730
好的
All right.

12:47.730 --> 12:50.100
-林肯  -什么
-Linc?  -Yeah?

12:50.100 --> 12:54.660
当天审判过后  我去福克斯河监狱看你
After your trial that day I came to see you at Fox River...

12:54.660 --> 12:55.860
怎么了
What about it?

12:55.860 --> 12:58.300
我认为是你干的
I thought you did it.

12:59.560 --> 13:02.430
我认为是你杀了特伦斯·斯特曼
I thought you killed Terrence Steadman.

13:02.430 --> 13:03.760
其他人也这么想吗
Along with everyone else?

13:03.760 --> 13:08.560
但我离开的时候
But by the time I left, I...

13:08.560 --> 13:10.300
我知道你是无辜的
I knew you were innocent.

13:10.300 --> 13:13.230
我一定要把你从里面弄出来
And I had to get you out of that place.

13:13.230 --> 13:16.100
不管这次结果怎样
So, however this plays out,

13:16.100 --> 13:19.300
我决不后悔
I have no regrets.

14:06.600 --> 14:08.330
斯科菲尔德在厕所藏了东西
Scofield's hiding something in the washroom.

14:08.330 --> 14:09.360
看来我们找到了
I think we just found

14:09.360 --> 14:11.600
缺失的"锡拉"部件了  给怀肯打电话
our missing piece of Scylla. Call Vikan.

14:11.600 --> 14:13.360
我要先跟我女儿通话
I want to talk to my daughter first.

14:13.360 --> 14:14.830
只管给怀肯打电话  她们没事
Just call him, okay, they're fine.

14:14.830 --> 14:18.100
我跟怀肯有过交易
I have a history with Vikan.

14:18.100 --> 14:20.860
如果我不告诉他你没问题  他是不会交易的
No money exchanges hands unless I tell him you're legit.

14:20.860 --> 14:23.230
我要跟我女儿通话  马上
I want to talk to my daughter. Now!

14:33.860 --> 14:35.100
喂
Yeah?

14:35.100 --> 14:36.660
让她女儿听电话
Put the daughter on the phone.

14:36.660 --> 14:38.100
有问题吗
Is there a problem?

14:38.100 --> 14:39.900
只管让她听电话
Just put her on the phone.

14:42.630 --> 14:43.730
喂
Hello?

14:43.730 --> 14:46.130
艾米丽  宝贝  我是格雷琴阿姨
Emily, baby, it's your Auntie Gretchen.

14:46.130 --> 14:47.260
你在哪
Where are you?

14:47.260 --> 14:49.360
不远的地方  你还好吗
I'm not far. Are you okay?

14:49.360 --> 14:51.400
这里有个坏人
There's this mean man here.

14:56.830 --> 14:58.960
艾米丽  宝贝  还记得
Emily, baby, do you remember the mean man

14:58.960 --> 15:00.700
以前跟你妈妈丽塔一起住的坏人吗
that used to live with your mommy Rita?

15:00.700 --> 15:02.060
那个对你大吼大叫的人
The one that used to yell at you all the time?

15:02.060 --> 15:03.060
罗伊吗
Roy?

15:03.060 --> 15:04.530
就是他
That's the one.

15:04.530 --> 15:06.130
罗伊最后怎么了
And what happened to Roy?

15:06.130 --> 15:07.560
有一天  他去商店
He went to the store one day

15:07.560 --> 15:10.030
就再没回来了
and never came back.

15:10.030 --> 15:11.660
没错
That's right.

15:11.660 --> 15:14.730
我觉得  如果你不喜欢这个坏人
And I think that if you don't like this mean man,

15:14.730 --> 15:17.800
很快  他就会走
then very soon, he's going to leave

15:17.800 --> 15:20.060
永远不会再回来
and he's never coming back.

15:20.060 --> 15:22.000
真的吗
You think so?

15:22.000 --> 15:22.860
宝贝  是真的
Baby, I know so.

15:22.860 --> 15:25.200
行了  够了
All right, that's enough.

15:25.200 --> 15:27.430
艾米丽  宝贝  让那个坏人接电话
Emily, baby, put the mean man back on the phone.

15:30.900 --> 15:32.900
听着  我两小时内给你打电话
Listen to me. I'm going to call you

15:32.900 --> 15:34.760
告诉你准确的交易地址
in two hours with the exact location of the exchange.

15:34.760 --> 15:35.930
如果我没打电话
If you don't hear from me,

15:35.930 --> 15:37.430
就把她们杀了
kill them both.

15:51.230 --> 15:53.430
你有客人吗
You expecting somebody?

15:53.430 --> 15:55.900
没有
No.

16:02.360 --> 16:04.800
自然点
Look lively.

16:04.800 --> 16:06.630
宝贝
Hey, buttercup, why don't you

16:06.630 --> 16:08.230
去房间玩吧
go play with your dollsies or something.

16:08.230 --> 16:11.330
没事的  宝贝  回房间玩吧
It's okay, honey. Go to your playroom.

16:17.860 --> 16:19.100
你们好
Hi, there.

16:19.100 --> 16:21.460
我叫拉尔夫·贝克  我是卖圣经的
My name is Ralph Becker, and I'm selling Bibles

16:21.460 --> 16:23.630
为圣三一教会筹集善款
to raise money for the Church of the Holy Trinity.

16:23.630 --> 16:25.000
不知你们能否花5分钟
And I wonder if I could spend five minutes

16:25.000 --> 16:27.130
我们谈谈福音
of your time and talk about the Gospel with you.

16:27.130 --> 16:31.360
拉尔夫  我们现在有点  不太方便
We're a bit, uh, indisposed at the moment, Ralph.

16:31.360 --> 16:32.760
明天再来吧
Can you come back tomorrow?

16:32.760 --> 16:35.330
今天是筹款的最后一天
Well, actually, today is the last day of the fund-raiser.

16:35.330 --> 16:36.930
我说我们很忙
I said we're busy.

16:36.930 --> 16:39.430
但总能为上帝抽出点时间吧
We're never too busy for God.

16:39.430 --> 16:41.400
在他的王国里
And what's a few minutes

16:41.400 --> 16:43.500
在下午抽出点时间  怎么样
of your afternoon for a place in His kingdom?

16:43.500 --> 16:46.830
朋友  你这圣经推销员可有点强求
You're a bit pushy for a Bible salesman, ain't you, friend?

16:47.900 --> 16:49.880
我有使命在身
I'm on a mission.

16:50.580 --> 16:52.560
你有使命在身  对吧
You're on a mission, right?

16:55.160 --> 16:57.100
-你在做什么  -关门
-What are you doing?!  -Close the door!

16:58.460 --> 17:00.030
-他是"公司"的人  -什么"公司"
-This guy is Company!  -What company?!

17:00.030 --> 17:00.860
拿绳子把他捆起来
Get me some rope to tie him up with.

17:00.860 --> 17:02.600
他只是个圣经推销员
This guy is a Bible salesman.

17:02.600 --> 17:04.730
去拿绳子  现在就去
Get me the rope, now!

17:35.030 --> 17:38.400
阿历克斯  很会选见面地点嘛
Good choice for a meeting spot, Alex.

17:38.400 --> 17:40.400
人多  两个出口
Crowded place. Two exits.

17:40.400 --> 17:43.230
墙角的座位  整个房间的动静尽收眼底
Corner table with a full view of the room.

17:43.230 --> 17:45.800
看来你习惯逃亡的生活了
Looks like you're getting acclimated to life on the run.

17:48.560 --> 17:51.330
听说你升职了
I hear you got promoted.

17:51.330 --> 17:53.130
有自己的办公室  惠勒
Your own field office, Wheeler.

17:53.130 --> 17:55.630
真是让人印象深刻
That's impressive.

17:55.630 --> 17:58.000
如果你不是丢了联调局的脸
When you're neither a disgrace to the Bureau

17:58.000 --> 18:00.130
或者犯毒瘾  你也能摊上这样的好事
nor a drug addict, good things can happen.

18:00.130 --> 18:01.160
他都戒掉了  马克
He's clean, Mark.

18:01.160 --> 18:02.630
谢谢提醒   费丽舍
Thank you, Felicia.

18:02.630 --> 18:04.700
我知道你为人  马克
Look, I know you, Mark.

18:04.700 --> 18:06.000
你是一名好特工  有雄心壮志
You're a good agent, ambitious.

18:06.000 --> 18:07.400
让我助你一臂之力
So, let me appeal to the side of you

18:07.400 --> 18:08.900
让你的名字上头条
that likes to see your name in print.

18:08.900 --> 18:12.000
想进副局长候选人名单吧
Want to be on a short list for Deputy Director? Huh?

18:12.000 --> 18:14.530
没错  朗格把我加进去了
Right. Lang filled me in.

18:14.530 --> 18:17.160
你原本已十拿九稳
You've got solid gold intel.

18:17.160 --> 18:20.230
我不知道我是否比一个被炒的联调员
I don't know if I'm more skeptical of a burned out ex-Fed

18:20.230 --> 18:23.200
或一个被称为"公司"的神秘组织让人怀疑
or the mythical cabal known as the Company.

18:23.200 --> 18:25.830
你大老远来就为了个秘密
You came all the way here for a myth?

18:28.600 --> 18:30.760
你想怎样  阿历克斯
What do you want, Alex?

18:30.760 --> 18:33.360
费丽舍跟我说你是司法部长的耳目
Felicia tells me you have the attorney general's ear.

18:33.360 --> 18:34.560
没错
That's right.

18:34.560 --> 18:38.730
联调局在密谋交易
The Bureau is compromised.

18:38.730 --> 18:41.700
国安局也在密谋交易
Homeland Security is compromised.

18:41.700 --> 18:44.530
我要一个我能信任的人  我能相信你吗
I need someone I can trust. Can I trust you?

18:50.930 --> 18:55.260
你能给我打垮"公司"的可靠情报
You get me credible intelligence against the Company...

18:55.260 --> 18:57.260
我就亲自
I'll walk you into the

18:57.260 --> 19:00.530
去找司法部长
attorney general's office myself.

19:02.300 --> 19:04.230
我们会拿到的
We'll get it.

19:17.730 --> 19:19.930
阿历克斯  说吧
Alex, talk to me.

19:19.930 --> 19:22.300
我在政府里找到能相信的人了
I think I found someone in government we can trust.

19:22.300 --> 19:24.100
你们还要多久才能拿到"锡拉"
How close are you to getting Scylla?

19:24.100 --> 19:26.560
-快了  -迈克尔
Very. Michael...

19:26.560 --> 19:29.130
我们这有委托人  你们一定得搞定才行
We're in escrow here. You've got to come through with the house.

19:29.130 --> 19:30.630
别担心
Don't worry.

19:30.630 --> 19:32.160
我们就快拿到"锡拉"了
We're getting Scylla.

19:32.160 --> 19:35.030
好吧
All right.

19:35.860 --> 19:37.400
看我找到什么了
Look what I found.

19:37.400 --> 19:39.560
问题是  没法用来射他们
Problem is, there's no way to shoot them.

19:46.260 --> 19:48.630
可以
Yeah, we do.

19:48.630 --> 19:52.530
但需要你去买点发胶和打火机
But i need you to buy some hairspray and a lighter.

20:07.300 --> 20:09.730
这是什么
What's this?

20:09.730 --> 20:11.700
我的辞呈
My resignation.

20:13.460 --> 20:17.030
丽莎  我已经够保护你
Lisa, I tried to shield you from everything

20:17.030 --> 20:18.500
不让你做无法胜任的事
I didn't think you could handle.

20:18.500 --> 20:20.660
你唯一保护我的事
The only thing you shielded me from

20:20.660 --> 20:22.500
是不让我知道你真正的为人
was knowing who you really are.

20:23.830 --> 20:25.560
我现在知道了
Now I know.

20:27.300 --> 20:29.430
我原本想要个儿子
I wanted a son.

20:30.200 --> 20:33.360
长官
Sir...

20:33.360 --> 20:35.400
一小时前拍到的
Taken less than an hour ago.

20:35.400 --> 20:39.030
你是对的  格雷琴和赛尔夫在一起
You were right-- Gretchen's with Self.

20:44.000 --> 20:46.770
你们的任务是安全地拿回"锡拉"
Your mission is the safe retrieval of Scylla.

20:46.770 --> 20:48.000
任务的限制呢
one of the Rules of engagement?

20:48.000 --> 20:50.000
格杀勿论
there are none shoot on side

20:50.000 --> 20:52.300
方特罗伊酒店  在市中心
Fauntleroy Hotel, downtown.

21:05.620 --> 21:07.050
谁派你来的
Who sent you?!

21:07.050 --> 21:08.650
圣三一教会
The Church of The Holy Trinity.

21:08.650 --> 21:09.450
说谎
Liar!

21:09.450 --> 21:11.250
你疯了吗
Are you out of your mind?!

21:11.250 --> 21:12.250
你在打一个
You're beating up

21:12.250 --> 21:13.280
圣经推销员
a Bible salesman!

21:13.280 --> 21:14.580
我不是斯科菲尔德
I ain't Scofield.

21:14.580 --> 21:15.920
我也不是布伦斯
I ain't Burrows.

21:15.920 --> 21:17.220
我不是我的命运  干嘛要来找我
This ain't my lot! Leave me alone!

21:17.220 --> 21:18.950
我不是什么
I'm not a part of this

21:18.950 --> 21:20.650
"公司"的人
Company!

21:20.650 --> 21:21.750
我什么都不知道  我发誓
I don't know anything, I swear.

21:21.750 --> 21:22.980
看看他  求求你  看他
Look at him! Please, please, just look at him!

21:22.980 --> 21:24.550
难道他看起来像
Does he look like some kind

21:24.550 --> 21:26.050
什么卧底吗
of a undercover agent to you?!

21:26.050 --> 21:27.820
他们很会掩人耳目
They blend in!

21:27.820 --> 21:28.980
这就是为什么他们能抓到你
That's how they get you!

21:28.980 --> 21:30.280
看这个  他的钱包  行吧
Look at this.Okay, his wallet, okay?

21:30.280 --> 21:31.380
他有加州的驾驶执照
He's got a California driver's license.

21:31.380 --> 21:32.580
拉尔夫·贝克
"Ralph Becker," okay?

21:32.580 --> 21:35.180
他还有借书卡和祈祷卡
He's got a library card and a prayer card.

21:35.180 --> 21:36.320
这够说服力了吧
That is pretty convincing.

21:36.320 --> 21:37.280
看看
Look at this.

21:37.280 --> 21:38.980
自由  荣誉  国家
"Freedom, Honor, Country.

21:38.980 --> 21:41.080
东南军校  98届
Southeastern Military Academy, Class of '98."

21:41.080 --> 21:44.120
有多少圣经推销员
How many Bible salesman do you know graduate

21:44.120 --> 21:45.780
是从军校毕业的
from a military academy?!

21:45.780 --> 21:48.950
不是的  我没去东南军校  这是我弟弟的戒指
No! I didn't go to Southeastern! It's my kid brother's ring!

21:48.950 --> 21:51.420
他去年在巴格达死了
He died in Baghdad last year!

21:51.420 --> 21:53.550
死于汽车爆炸事件
It was a car bomb!

21:53.550 --> 21:56.320
我发誓
I swear!

21:56.320 --> 21:58.380
听我说
Listen to me.

21:59.480 --> 22:01.120
这么说是真的
That made sense.

22:01.120 --> 22:03.680
行了吧
Okay...

22:03.680 --> 22:05.480
这讲得通
that made sense.

22:05.480 --> 22:06.820
求你了
Please!

22:12.520 --> 22:14.020
除非我接到电话
We're not going nowhere!

22:14.020 --> 22:16.320
我们哪儿都不许去
Not till I get a phone call!

22:25.520 --> 22:28.220
一小时25美元
It's $25 for the hour.

22:28.220 --> 22:30.950
我们不是来开房的
We don't need a room.

22:30.950 --> 22:32.480
我在找我姐姐
I, uh, I'm looking for my sister.

22:32.480 --> 22:33.620
她的名字是格雷琴·摩根
Her name's Gretchen Morgan.

22:33.620 --> 22:35.320
你能告诉我她住哪间房吗
Can you tell me what room she's in?

22:35.320 --> 22:37.450
你想查什么  就打411
You want information, call 411.

22:42.320 --> 22:44.220
现在呢
How about now?

22:46.820 --> 22:48.780
没有叫格雷琴·摩根的人
No Gretchen Morgan.

22:48.780 --> 22:50.850
没有退款
No refund.

22:50.850 --> 22:52.980
她差不多五尺七
She's about five-seven.

22:52.980 --> 22:54.580
黑头发和蓝眼睛
She's got black hair and blue eyes,

22:54.580 --> 22:56.050
我想她在这么"漂亮"的旅店
and I imagine she'd stand out

22:56.050 --> 22:58.120
里一定很抢眼
in a fine establishment like this one.

23:05.520 --> 23:06.850
308房
Room 308.

23:06.850 --> 23:08.850
非常感谢
Thank you so much.

23:11.220 --> 23:13.980
不准在楼道尿尿
No urinating in the stairwell.

23:13.980 --> 23:16.820
这是明文规定
That's the golden rule.

23:19.750 --> 23:21.620
喂
Yeah?

23:21.620 --> 23:22.850
他们在三楼
Yeah, they're on the third floor,

23:22.850 --> 23:23.850
从旅店正面看
front of the hotel,

23:23.850 --> 23:25.280
就在中间的左边
just to the left of center.

23:26.080 --> 23:28.350
收到  谢谢
Got it, thanks.

23:29.450 --> 23:31.150
在三楼  阳台左边
Third floor up, just left of the balcony.

23:32.750 --> 23:37.420
就装在那边楼顶上吧
Why don't you set up on that rooftop over there?

23:42.450 --> 23:43.750
"锡拉"已经快搞定了
Scylla's almost complete.

23:43.750 --> 23:44.850
你那头准备好了吗
Is everything ready on your end?

23:44.850 --> 23:46.250
让我跟格雷琴谈
Let me talk to Gretchen.

23:46.250 --> 23:47.720
不  你跟我谈
No, you're talking to me.

23:47.720 --> 23:49.650
买家已经到了
The buyer has touched down.

23:49.650 --> 23:51.720
他们可没耐性等你
This isn't the kind of person you keep waiting.

23:51.720 --> 23:52.950
我也一样
Likewise.

23:52.950 --> 23:54.280
让他们把钱准备好
Just make sure he has the money ready.

23:54.280 --> 23:55.650
听着  臭小子
Listen to me, you mook.

23:55.650 --> 23:57.450
你现在已在深水区
You're in the deep end of the pool now.

23:57.450 --> 23:59.180
至少装着你会游泳
At least act like you can swim.

23:59.180 --> 24:01.720
下次打电话时  我要和格雷琴说话
And the next time I call, I want to talk to Gretchen.

24:01.720 --> 24:02.980
不  你听我说
No, no, no, you listen to me, okay?

24:02.980 --> 24:04.450
下次你打过来
The next time you call, it better be

24:04.450 --> 24:06.820
最好告诉我钱准备好了  懂了吗
to tell me that the money's ready, you understand?

24:10.480 --> 24:11.580
喂
Hello.

24:11.580 --> 24:12.820
我想让你知道
I thought you should know

24:12.820 --> 24:15.480
有一个男的和一个女的来找你了
a man and a woman came in looking for you.

24:15.480 --> 24:17.320
-斯科菲尔德找到我们了  -怎么可能
Scofield found us. How?

24:17.320 --> 24:18.320
我不管  做好准备
Who cares? Just get ready.

24:18.320 --> 24:19.580
多久前的事
How long ago?

24:19.580 --> 24:21.050
几分钟
A couple of minutes.

24:27.250 --> 24:30.520
我可不想我的地方有麻烦
I don't want no trouble in my place!

25:19.780 --> 25:21.180
我去检查一下走廊
I'm gonna recon the hallway.

25:21.180 --> 25:23.020
有情况的话  带上"锡拉"离开
Anything goes down, get Scylla, get out.

25:23.020 --> 25:24.150
我会去找你
I will find you.

25:24.150 --> 25:25.720
好的
Okay.

28:22.420 --> 28:27.120
迈克尔  就像我说的  这只是笔交易
Michael, like I said before, this is just business.

28:27.120 --> 28:30.250
我的耳朵
My ear!

28:30.250 --> 28:32.150
不许动
Don't move!

28:32.720 --> 28:33.990
上车
Get in!

28:48.790 --> 28:51.790
帮我把他抬到车厢里
Help me get him in the back of the van!

29:01.450 --> 29:03.520
迈克尔
Michael!

29:20.090 --> 29:21.250
那是什么
What is that?

29:21.250 --> 29:23.720
是仓库
It's the warehouse.

29:24.690 --> 29:26.220
那个芯片
The chip.

29:33.820 --> 29:35.190
你确定在这儿
You sure it's here?

29:35.420 --> 29:36.990
是  我确定
Yeah, I'm sure.

29:36.990 --> 29:40.250
从图上看  只可能在一个地方
From the schematic, it can only be in one place.

30:04.290 --> 30:07.450
别犯傻  好吧  格雷琴
Look, don't be stupid, okay, Gretchen?

30:07.450 --> 30:11.020
你能要回你的女儿和钱
You're gonna get your daughter back and your money.

30:11.020 --> 30:14.650
我在车上等你
I'll see you in the car.

30:29.250 --> 30:31.050
他被带来时就这样
He was brought in like this.

30:31.050 --> 30:32.750
谁在那儿
Who's there?

30:34.720 --> 30:36.350
我给他注射十毫升氯硝安定
